snippet.title: Imaginary Friend Asylum | Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2643930/Imaginary_Friend_Asylum/

Imaginary Friend Asylum is finally here! In this psychological horror game, you play a child in an insane asylum. You're in a cruel world but your imaginary friends have your back. Here, you will uncover a dark conspiracy where you are to receive a terrible fate.

© 2024 Grant Marrs
